WEBVTT

00:00:00.804 --> 00:00:03.808
Upatmi nu le pa hna, 
TED ahhin thithruainak le cawlcanghnak

00:00:03.832 --> 00:00:05.413
thawkning tampi kan chim ve.

00:00:05.437 --> 00:00:07.851
Cuca'h, cawlcanghnak thawkning 
hram in dongh tiang

00:00:07.875 --> 00:00:09.119
minute 3 chungah zoh u sih

00:00:09.143 --> 00:00:10.976
i, cu chungin cawnnak ilak hna u sih.

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:12.358
Ahmasaah, nan hngalh bangin

00:00:12.382 --> 00:00:15.800
hruaitu nih intuarnak
caah ralthatnak aherh.

00:00:17.463 --> 00:00:19.261
Zohmanh, a tuahmi hi zulh a fawite.

00:00:19.285 --> 00:00:21.649
Hi ahhin a zultu hmasa
nih biapi thil a tuah;

00:00:21.673 --> 00:00:23.976
Hnuzulh dan kha 
hawidang a hmuhsak hna.

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:26.555
Amah cu hruaitu nih hruaitu
bangin a upat kan hmuh;

00:00:26.579 --> 00:00:28.524
Atu cu hruaitu kong asi ti lai lo;

00:00:28.548 --> 00:00:29.976
Anmah kong asi lai, atammi.